 2023-03532023-04-21JUS
ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisAppointment of the HONOURABLE JANE A. FAGNAN, a Justice of the Court of King’s Bench of Alberta, to be a Justice of Appeal of the Court of Appeal of Alberta, and a Judge ex officio of the Court of King's Bench of Alberta; and to be a Judge of the Court of Appeal of the Northwest Territories and a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Nunavut during her tenure of office as a Justice of Appeal of the Court of Appeal of Alberta.
